%N A315477 Coordination sequence Gal.5.293.3 where Gal.u.t.v denotes the coordination sequence for a vertex of type v in tiling number t in the Galebach list of u-uniform tilings.
%C A315477 Note that there may be other vertices in the Galebach list of u-uniform tilings with u <= 6 that have this same coordination sequence. See the Galebach link for the complete list of A-numbers for all these tilings.
%H A315477 Brian Galebach, <a href="/A250120/a250120.html">k-uniform tilings (k <= 6) and their A-numbers</a>
%F A315477 Conjectures from _Jianing Song_, Jun 02 2026: (Start)
%F A315477 a(n) = a(n-5) + 27 for n >= 6.
%F A315477 G.f.: (1 + 5*x + 5*x^2 + 5*x^3 + 5*x^4 + 5*x^5 + x^6) / ((1 - x)^2*(1 + x + x^2 + x^3 + x^4)). (End)
%F A315477 Conjecture: a(n) ~ 27*n/5. - _Stefano Spezia_, Jun 02 2026
